Title: The Prince & Me 3: A Royal Honeymoon
Actors: Kam Heskin, Chris Geere, Adam Croasdell, Jonathan Firth
Plot: King Edvard, to please Queen Paige, diverts their honeymoon to the fictional crown protectorate of Belavia. Soon they discover an underhanded plot by the ambitious Danish prime minister; hijinks abound, but Eddie, Paige, and Belavia win.
